| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3743 — Recovery Inhibition (dAn0n)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cf1ee26c-efa7-5ff2-bea3-1995e35aff0b"
